  "title": "Recruiter (WFH, Remote Support)/ Call Support -  Commission based",
  "description": "<p><strong>Recruiter (WFH, Remote Support)/ Call Support/ Telemarketer - Commission based</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Calling for Supermoms, Superdaddy, Superhero YOU!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>YES! You are THE ONE! We are hiring Recruiter (WFH, Remote Support)/ Call Support/ Telemarketer) </strong>who are keen to take on flexible-work arrangement as a Recruiter cum Telemarketer.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We want you and we would like to journey with you to help you achieve your next career purpose that commensurate with an attractive benefit/ Commission and an integrated work life harmony.</p>\n<p>Come, join our Team!</p>\n<p>Interested applicants, we are waiting for you… wait no further and send over your MS word resume over to us.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Good track record in providing Customer Service/ Telemarketer.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Proven experience as Recruitment Consultant, HR Consultant or similar position will be an added advantage</strong></li>\n  <li>Min. 2 years of Customer Service/ Telemarketer/ Cold-calling in a Call Centre environment experience.</li>\n  <li>Experience working as a <strong>Telemarketer in a Bank or Contact Centre environment is highly desirable.</strong></li>\n  <li>Able to communicate effectively and professionally over the phone.</li>\n  <li>Confident and pleasant personality</li>\n  <li>Enjoy talking to people over the phone.</li>\n  <li>Willing to learn the traits of recruitment.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and as a team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>**Incumbent must be CEI Certified or willing to go for the CEI course is required.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Candidate must be willing to take on a Commission base role.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence your update MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p>\n<p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
